OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,6,Flight rain, but some drier and
OL,7,Fbrighter spells developing in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Outbreaks of rain will then
OL,9,Fspread northeast late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fa few showery outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Fspreading northeast. The rain will be
OL,14,Fmostly light and patchy, but perhaps
OL,15,Fheavier for a time this evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAny early morning rain will
OL,18,Fquickly clear away. Otherwise a bright
OL,19,Fday with sunny spells and a few
OL,20,Fscattered showers, one or two on the
OL,21,Fheavy side in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
