OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FAn
OL,6,Funsettled and changeable few days
OL,7,Fahead. Often rather cloudy, with bands
OL,8,Fof showers or longer spells of rain,
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy
